  // FRONTIER CRAWL (user: 'pick a BIG chunk and GO there'): the fog-gated path dead-ends at the dark edge
  // ('Terrain path: 2 wp') while the bucket sits beyond it -- the walk stopped closing, the 9s stall banned the
